#originalTopic=does-owning-a-gun-make-you-safer
People with guns are not one bit safer - because if someone else knows they have this gun, they can simply surprise them from behind, and suddenly - another armed criminal is loose.  As far as I am concerned, people who apply for gun permits - have already failed a psychological stability test, for wanting a gun in the first place.  